           tree-drag-source-row-draggable) :boolean
 #+liber-documentation
 "@version{#2021-3-5}
  @argument[source]{a @class{gtk:tree-drag-source} object}
  @argument[path]{a @class{gtk:tree-path} instance with the row on which user
